</div></div></div></div></div><div id="about" class="content-block row wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1763401422059 bg-white"><div class="container"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12 vc_hidden-xs"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><header class='content-heading'>
						<h2 class='main-heading'>Cruising Adventures</h2>
						<div class='main-subtitle'><p><em>&#8220;Let me drive the boat!&#8221;</em></p>
</div>
						<div class='seperator'></div>
					</header><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1762631919017"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12 vc_hidden-xs"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="cq-sidebyside-container  cq-sidebyside-leftright" data-card1titlecolor="#ffffff" data-card1contentcolor="#ffffff" data-card1bg="#bddbff" data-card2titlecolor="" data-card2contentcolor="" data-card2bg="#ffffff" data-dividerbg="#ffffff" data-dividercolor="#333333" data-card1iconsize="" data-cardheight="380px" data-dividerborder="50%" data-dividerfontsize="" data-dividerwidth="" data-dividerheight="" data-contentsize="16px" data-titlesize="20px" data-contentwidth="" data-card2iconsize="" data-elementwidth="" data-cardmargin="" data-card1avatar="" data-card2avatar="image" data-tooltipposition="top" data-cardshape="" data-isgap="cq-isgap" data-gapcolor="" data-carddirection="leftright" data-followyoffset=""><div class="cq-sidebyside-content cq-isgap cq-sidecontent-1" data-cardtitle="" data-cardavatar="" data-iconcolor=""><div class="cq-sidebyside-paragraphy"  data-image=""><span class="cq-sidebyside-text">Embark on an unforgettable adventure with Cruising Adventures! Take the wheel of your own speedboat and explore Nassau’s stunning waters on a thrilling guided tour that combines speed boating and snorkeling. Start from our private dock with easy instructions, then follow our expert guides to the island’s most breathtaking spots. Safe, exciting, and family-friendly — it’s the ultimate Bahamian experience!</span></div></div><div class="cq-sidebyside-content cq-isgap cq-sidecontent-2" data-cardtitle="" data-cardavatar="image" data-iconcolor=""><div class="cq-sidebyside-paragraphy" data-image="https://cruisingadventuresltd.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Untitled-design-1.jpg"><div class="cq-sidebyside-imgcontainer"></div><span class="cq-sidebyside-text">Experience the thrill of the Bahamas with Cruising Adventures LTD, Nassau’s premier speed boat tour company. Located near Arawak Cay, we offer fun, safe, and unforgettable adventures perfect for couples, families, and thrill-seekers. No license or experience needed — drive your own boat across crystal-clear waters as our certified guides lead you to hidden beaches, stunning coastlines, and vibrant marine life. Each tour includes safety briefings, life jackets, and full support from our expert team. Just minutes from downtown Nassau and cruise ports, Cruising Adventures LTD delivers one of the island’s top-rated excursions — combining freedom, excitement, and breathtaking ocean views in every ride.</span></div></div></div>
	<div class="wpb_raw_code wpb_content_element wpb_raw_html" >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<a href="https://tourphotos.com/cruisingadventures" target="_blank" style="display:block; text-decoration:none;">
  <div style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-top: 27.7778%; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px 0 rgba(63,69,81,0.16); margin-top: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.9em; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 8px; will-change: transform;">
    <iframe loading="lazy" 
